  </span>
</div>
```

**MUST NOT:**

- ❌ Use inline styles (except for dynamic values)
- ❌ Mix Tailwind classes with inline styles unnecessarily
- ❌ Create custom CSS when Tailwind utilities exist
- ❌ Use arbitrary values when standard utilities exist

